{
  "video_id": "LV-RvzXGH2Y",
  "title": "Mike Matas: A next-generation digital book",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 17259.0,
      "text": "So for the past year and a half,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17260.0,
      "end_time": 19260.0,
      "text": "my team at Push Pop Press"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19260.0,
      "end_time": 21260.0,
      "text": "and Charlie Melcher and Melcher Media"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "have been working on creating"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 25260.0,
      "text": "the first feature-length interactive book."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25260.0,
      "end_time": 27260.0,
      "text": "It's called \"Our Choice\""
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27260.0,
      "end_time": 29260.0,
      "text": "and the author is Al Gore."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 29260.0,
      "end_time": 31260.0,
      "text": "It's the sequel to \"An Inconvenient Truth,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 31260.0,
      "end_time": 33260.0,
      "text": "and it explores all the solutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 33260.0,
      "end_time": 35260.0,
      "text": "that will solve the climate crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 35260.0,
      "end_time": 38260.0,
      "text": "The book starts like this. This is the cover."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39260.0,
      "end_time": 41260.0,
      "text": "As the globe spins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41260.0,
      "end_time": 43260.0,
      "text": "we can see our location,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 43260.0,
      "end_time": 46260.0,
      "text": "and we can open the book"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 46260.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "and swipe through the chapters"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 50260.0,
      "text": "to browse the book."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 54260.0,
      "text": "Or, we can scroll through the pages at the bottom."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55260.0,
      "end_time": 57260.0,
      "text": "And if we wanted to zoom into a page,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57260.0,
      "end_time": 59260.0,
      "text": "we can just open it up."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "And anything you see in the book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 63260.0,
      "text": "you can pick up with two fingers"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 65259.0,
      "text": "and lift off the page"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 65260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67260.0,
      "text": "and open up."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 67260.0,
      "end_time": 69260.0,
      "text": "And if you want to go back"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 69260.0,
      "end_time": 71260.0,
      "text": "and read the book again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 71260.0,
      "end_time": 74260.0,
      "text": "you just fold it back up and put it back on the page."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 75260.0,
      "end_time": 78260.0,
      "text": "And so this works the same way; you pick it up and pop it open."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 78260.0,
      "end_time": 80260.0,
      "text": "(Audio) Al Gore: I consider myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 80260.0,
      "end_time": 82260.0,
      "text": "among the majority"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 82260.0,
      "end_time": 84260.0,
      "text": "who look at windmills and feel"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 84260.0,
      "end_time": 86260.0,
      "text": "they're a beautiful addition to the landscape."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 86260.0,
      "end_time": 88260.0,
      "text": "Mike Matas: And so throughout the whole book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 88260.0,
      "end_time": 91260.0,
      "text": "Al Gore will walk you through and explain the photos."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 91260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "This photo, you can you can even see on an interactive map."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 95260.0,
      "end_time": 98260.0,
      "text": "Zoom into it and see where it was taken."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 100260.0,
      "end_time": 102260.0,
      "text": "And throughout the book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 102260.0,
      "end_time": 104260.0,
      "text": "there's over an hour of documentary footage"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 104260.0,
      "end_time": 106260.0,
      "text": "and interactive animations."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 106260.0,
      "end_time": 109260.0,
      "text": "So you can open this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 109260.0,
      "end_time": 112260.0,
      "text": "(Audio) AG: Most modern wind turbines consist of a large ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 112260.0,
      "end_time": 114260.0,
      "text": "MM: It starts playing immediately."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 114260.0,
      "end_time": 117260.0,
      "text": "And while it's playing, we can pinch and peak back at the page,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 117260.0,
      "end_time": 119260.0,
      "text": "and the movie keeps playing."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 119260.0,
      "end_time": 122260.0,
      "text": "Or we can zoom out to the table of contents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 122260.0,
      "end_time": 125260.0,
      "text": "and the video keeps playing."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 127260.0,
      "end_time": 129259.0,
      "text": "But one of the coolest things in this book"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 129258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131260.0,
      "text": "are the interactive infographics."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 131260.0,
      "end_time": 133260.0,
      "text": "This one shows the wind potential"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 133260.0,
      "end_time": 135260.0,
      "text": "all around the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 135260.0,
      "end_time": 138260.0,
      "text": "But instead of just showing us the information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 138260.0,
      "end_time": 141260.0,
      "text": "we can take our finger and explore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 141260.0,
      "end_time": 143260.0,
      "text": "and see, state by state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 143260.0,
      "end_time": 145260.0,
      "text": "exactly how much wind potential there is."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 145260.0,
      "end_time": 148260.0,
      "text": "We can do the same for geothermal energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 150260.0,
      "end_time": 152260.0,
      "text": "and solar power."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 158260.0,
      "end_time": 160260.0,
      "text": "This is one of my favorites."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 160260.0,
      "end_time": 163260.0,
      "text": "So this shows ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 169260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 169260.0,
      "end_time": 171260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 171260.0,
      "end_time": 173260.0,
      "text": "When the wind is blowing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 173260.0,
      "end_time": 176260.0,
      "text": "any excess energy coming from the windmill"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "is diverted into the battery."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 180260.0,
      "text": "And as the wind starts dying down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 180260.0,
      "end_time": 182260.0,
      "text": "any excess energy will be diverted back into the house --"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 182260.0,
      "end_time": 185260.0,
      "text": "the lights never go out."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 191260.0,
      "text": "And this whole book, it doesn't just run on the iPad."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 191260.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "It also runs on the iPhone."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 194260.0,
      "end_time": 196260.0,
      "text": "And so you can start reading on your iPad in your living room"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 198260.0,
      "text": "and then pick up where you left off on the iPhone."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 200260.0,
      "text": "And it works the exact same way."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 200260.0,
      "end_time": 202260.0,
      "text": "You can pinch into any page."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 202260.0,
      "end_time": 204260.0,
      "text": "Open it up."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 218260.0,
      "end_time": 220260.0,
      "text": "So that's Push Pop Press' first title,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 220260.0,
      "end_time": 222260.0,
      "text": "Al Gore's \"Our Choice.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 222260.0,
      "end_time": 224260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 224260.0,
      "end_time": 232260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 232260.0,
      "end_time": 235260.0,
      "text": "Chris Anderson: That's spectacular."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 235260.0,
      "end_time": 237260.0,
      "text": "Do you want to be a publisher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 237260.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "a technology licenser?"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 241260.0,
      "text": "What is the business here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 241260.0,
      "end_time": 243260.0,
      "text": "Is this something that other people can do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 243260.0,
      "end_time": 245260.0,
      "text": "MM: Yeah, we're building a tool"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 245260.0,
      "end_time": 248260.0,
      "text": "that makes it really easy for publishers right now to build this content."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 248260.0,
      "end_time": 250260.0,
      "text": "So Melcher Media's team, who's on the East coast --"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 250260.0,
      "end_time": 253260.0,
      "text": "and we're on the West coast, building the software --"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 253260.0,
      "end_time": 255260.0,
      "text": "takes our tool"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 255260.0,
      "end_time": 258260.0,
      "text": "and, every day, drags in images and text."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 258260.0,
      "end_time": 261260.0,
      "text": "CA: So you want to license this software to publishers"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 261260.0,
      "end_time": 263260.0,
      "text": "to make books as beautiful as that? (MM: Yes.)"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 263260.0,
      "end_time": 265260.0,
      "text": "All right. Mike, thanks so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 265260.0,
      "end_time": 267260.0,
      "text": "MM: Thank you. (CA: Good luck.)"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 267260.0,
      "end_time": 269260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}